---
title: Sesame Chicken Schnitzel & Cauli-Potato Mash with BBQ-Sriracha Sauce & Cucumber Slaw
description: It’s a twist on chicken schnitzel, we’re combining sriracha with BBQ sauce so the schnitzels are extra mouth-watering when this sauce is drizzled over. This dish becomes more alluring when you catch sight of the fluffy cauli-potato mash. There's no way you could miss this dish!

